Program: Letter from America by Alistair Cooke
Title: Consequences of the Disability Act
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/p00yjg06
Last Broadcast Date: Fri 10 Apr 1998
The consequences Americans with Disabilities Act of 1990, the influence of the civil courts on pro-golf and a 9 year old girl's debunking of Therapeutic Touch.